to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200mearlier\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old had gone into the event hoping to win his second gold of the games, having previously done so in the 100m last weekend.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 400, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"his second gold\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Lyles was forced to settle for bronze with the Team USA star later falling to the ground.Now, his mother Keisha Caine Bishop has alleged that stadium security initially refused to call a doctor for the sprinter.View this post on InstagramA post shared by Keisha Bishop (@keisha_caine_bishop)Writing on Instagram, she wrote: \\\"This was one of the scariest moments of my life!\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 516, \"end\": 521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9963216817912843, \"rank\": 0.0036824516224041965, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 563, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9997572868921137, \"rank\": 0.0002427266878230634, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}, {\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 640, \"t