\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They also refused to do anything to help.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They totally ignored me!\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No parent should ever have to experience this feeling of helplessness!\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No parent\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"this feeling\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"helplessness\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"However, I want to thank the @nbcolympics team for helping me during this moment.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the @nbcolympics team\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you for seeing me & my son as human beings and not just another story.JUST IN:Jack Carlin update as Team GB star involved in horror cycling clash at Paris Olympics\\\"Words cannot express my gratitude for your empathy, professionalism, and kindness.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"score\": 0.6161608834736579, \"rank\": 0.6228591880641084, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Shephard\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Carlin\", \"score\": 0.7998890933453702, \"rank\": 0.25017331567527307, \"text\": \"Carlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Carlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Carlin\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"htt